  npcName: Bagisant Offondront
  dialogueLines:
  - 'It''s still warm.

    That means you''re alive too.'
  - Light returns, but something's always missing. Always.
  - "The Core doesn\u2019t speak with words.\nIt answers with continuance."
  - "As long as it stands, so do you.\nDon\u2019t forget that."
  recipesToUnlock: []
  ambientDialogue:
  - "I do not sleep. I only\u2026 root"
  - "Don\u2019t look at the dark too long. It looks back."
  - Rest while the light holds. It burns fuel to keep you warm.
  - The crystals on my back are humming. The Core is happy.
